<dl id="n05045a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05045a">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05045a"> 45(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ up stones on Sabbath</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"> And yet they say that that was done on account of the hardness of their hearts; and that was done in a community where the law was so fierce that <mark>it stoned a man to death for picking up sticks on Sunday</mark>. <small> R.G. Ingersoll, <a name="MOSES" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#MOSES"><cite title="source">Some Mistakes of Moses</cite></a>, (1879) 14</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
